UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你殺了鬼嚎。你這個傻瓜!' WHERE entry=521; /* Text0_0: You killed Ghost Howl.  You\'re a stud! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='年輕的$c，靠近一點。我年輕的時候耳朵可好使了，但現在你必須大聲說話我才能聽到。' WHERE entry=522; /* Text0_0: Come closer, young one.  In my time I could hear the flutter of a prey\'s beating heart, but now you must speak up if you want your words heard. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='我在這片平原上生活了很多很多年，我捕獵過許多兇猛的野獸，從來沒有失敗過...直到我遇見了鬼嚎。$B$B很久以前，這只巨狼曾經是牛頭人的盟友，還和燃燒軍團英勇作戰。不過後來它被一個惡魔所傷，身上的傷口一直沒有治癒。最後...這道傷口把它逼瘋了。$B$B現在它總是痛苦地在平原上遊蕩，尋找終止它的痛苦的方法。我很慚愧，因為我無力把他殺掉...' WHERE entry=523; /* Text0_0: I have run through these plains for many, many seasons.  And I have hunted great beasts.  And I had never been bested... until I faced Ghost Howl.$B$BLong ago, the massive wolf was an ally to the tauren and fought bravely against the Burning Legion.  But he was wounded savagely by a demon, and the tear in his flesh never healed.  Eventually... it drove Ghost Howl mad.$B$BNow he roams the plains in agony, seeking an end to his pain.  To my shame, when we fought I lacked the strength to slay him... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你好啊，法師。我能在魔法知識的學習上為你提供什麼幫助嗎?',Text0_1_loc5='你好啊，法師。我能在魔法知識的學習上為你提供什麼幫助嗎?' WHERE entry=538; /* Text0_0: Greetings mage.  Shall I provide you with further insight into the world of magic? */ /* Text0_1: Greetings mage.  Shall I provide you with further insight into the world of magic? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='很高興見到你，$c。我給你的建議是:當你在世界旅行的時候，要當心魔法可能會傷害那些未受訓練的人。',Text0_1_loc5='很高興見到你，$c。我給你的建議是:當你在世界旅行的時候，要當心魔法可能會傷害那些未受訓練的人。' WHERE entry=539; /* Text0_0: Well met, $c.  My advice to you is this: as you travel the world, be wary of magic for it will burn the untrained. */ /* Text0_1: Well met, $c.  My advice to you is this: as you travel the world, be wary of magic for it will burn the untrained. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='很高興見到你，$c。我給你的建議是:當你在世界旅行的時候，要當心魔法可能會傷害那些未受訓練的人。',Text0_1_loc5='很高興見到你，$c。我給你的建議是:當你在世界旅行的時候，要當心魔法可能會傷害那些未受訓練的人。' WHERE entry=559; /* Text0_0: Well met, $c.  My advice to you is this: as you travel the world, be wary of magic for it will burn the untrained. */ /* Text0_1: Well met, $c.  My advice to you is this: as you travel the world, be wary of magic for it will burn the untrained. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你好。我是一個地精法師訓練師，而你是一個法師。',Text0_1_loc5='你好。我是一個地精法師訓練師，而你是一個法師。' WHERE entry=560; /* Text0_0: Greetings.  I\'m a gnome mage trainer, and you\'re a mage. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings.  I\'m a gnome mage trainer, and you\'re a mage. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='很高興見到你，$c。你想要一些忠告嗎?對法師好一點!我們的袖子裡面總可以變一兩個把戲，真的...',Text0_1_loc5='很高興見到你，$c。你想要一些忠告嗎?對法師好一點!我們的袖子裡面總可以變一兩個把戲，真的...' WHERE entry=561; /* Text0_0: Well met, $c.  You want some advice?  Befriend a mage!  We have a trick or two up our sleeves, we do... */ /* Text0_1: Well met, $c.  You want some advice?  Befriend a mage!  We have a trick or two up our sleeves, we do... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你好。我是一個不死族法師訓練師，而你是一個法師。',Text0_1_loc5='你好。我是一個不死族法師訓練師，而你是一個法師。' WHERE entry=562; /* Text0_0: Greetings.  I\'m an undead mage trainer, and you\'re a mage. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings.  I\'m an undead mage trainer, and you\'re a mage. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='很高興見到你，$c。我給你的建議是:當你在世界旅行的時候，要當心魔法可能會傷害那些未受訓練的人。',Text0_1_loc5='很高興見到你，$c。我給你的建議是:當你在世界旅行的時候，要當心魔法可能會傷害那些未受訓練的人。' WHERE entry=563; /* Text0_0: Well met, $c.  My advice to you is this: as you travel the world, be wary of magic for it will burn the untrained. */ /* Text0_1: Well met, $c.  My advice to you is this: as you travel the world, be wary of magic for it will burn the untrained. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你好，$c。你是來學習秘藏技藝的嗎?',Text0_1_loc5='你好，$c。你是來學習秘藏技藝的嗎?' WHERE entry=564; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.  Are you here to learn of the hidden arts? */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c.  Are you here to learn of the hidden arts? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='現在還不是讓你長眠的時候。我會幫你起死回生...但你也要為此付出一些代價。',Text0_1_loc5='現在還不是讓你長眠的時候。我會幫你起死回生...但你也要為此付出一些代價。' WHERE entry=580; /* Text0_0: It is not yet your time. I shall aid your journey back to the realm of the living... for a price. */ /* Text0_1: It is not yet your time. I shall aid your journey back to the realm of the living... for a price. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你要做什麼，$c?我快要遲到了，我的雇主不會給遲到的人好臉色看的。' WHERE entry=623; /* Text0_0: What do you want, $c? I\'m running late, and my employer doesn\'t look kindly on tardiness. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='是的，我是阿斯托·哈德恩。你是?' WHERE entry=624; /* Text0_0: Yes, I am. What\'s it to you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='看啊，竟然有個年輕的$c來看像我這樣的老農夫?' WHERE entry=678; /* Text0_0: What\'s a young $c like you out visiting an old farmer like me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='毒牙之王死了!我們還有希望!$b$b然而，整個喚醒儀式是非常複雜的，我無法獨自完成它。$b$b我現在就開始著手完成所有必要的準備工作，但與此同時，我需要你保護好我。通過翡翠夢境，在納拉雷克斯的夢魘中召喚出的怪物確實非常難纏。如果沒有你的幫助，這個任務對我來說會非常可怕。$b$b當你準備好要保護我的時候，就過來跟我說一聲，我會帶你到納拉雷克斯的房間去。' WHERE entry=699; /* Text0_0: The Fanglords are dead! All hope is not lost!$b$bThe awakening ritual is quite complex, however. It cannot be done alone.$b$bI will handle all of the necessary preparations but I will need you to protect me. The nightmares summoned from Naralex\'s journey through the Emerald Dream prove to be quite formidable. Without your help, this mission is doomed.$b$bWhen you are ready to defend me, say the word, and I shall lead the way to Naralex\'s chamber. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='機器調整了一下，面對著你。$B$B它的背後是空的，但是有一個奇怪的凹槽，上面寫著:「基爾卡克·旋杆的財產」' WHERE entry=718; /* Text0_0: The machine adjusts to face you.$B$BOn the back of the machine is an empty, oddly misshapen slot with an engraving that reads: "Propirtee o\' Cap\'n Gelkak Gyromast" */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='嘿!你在為提爾斯幹活嗎?如果我是你的話，我會離他遠遠的!酒精把他的大腦麻痺了，但是他的魔法還是和以前一樣厲害!' WHERE entry=720; /* Text0_0: Hey!  Are you on an errand for Tirth?  If I were you I\'d get as far away from him as I could!  His mind\'s been pickled from too much drink but his magic\'s as strong as ever! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='當然了，我會告訴你密碼的。只要你不讓提爾斯抓到我就行了!' WHERE entry=738; /* Text0_0: Sure, I\'ll tell you the phrase.  As long as I don\'t have to go anywhere near Tirth! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='基爾卡克的鑰匙滑到了縫隙中。' WHERE entry=758; /* Text0_0: Gelkak\'s key slides into the vacant slot. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='當我因為綁著這個大鐵球而不能保護自己的時候，你會嘲笑我嗎?' WHERE entry=759; /* Text0_0: Do you mock me while I am unable to defend myself, bound to this ball of iron? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='有個人類手中有能打開這個裝置的鑰匙。我想他的名字叫埃斯頓。' WHERE entry=760; /* Text0_0: One of the humans has the key to this infernal contraption. Eston I think they said his name was. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='從這裡離開，$c，不然他們也會把你鎖住的。' WHERE entry=761; /* Text0_0: Get away from here, $c, or they\'ll put you in chains as well. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='瑪爾根...他是一個獄卒。他應該有那把鑰匙。' WHERE entry=762; /* Text0_0: Marlgen... One of the jailors. He has the key to my bonds. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='我希望雪融化掉。它總是把我的長袍弄濕，把一切都搞得亂糟糟的!' WHERE entry=766; /* Text0_0: I wish the snow would just all melt away. It\'s always getting my robe wet and messing up everything! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='該死的雪...哦，你是...$n，是嗎?剛剛還有人跟我打聽你的事情呢。' WHERE entry=767; /* Text0_0: Stupid snow... Hey, you\'re, $n, aren\'t you? I\'ve just received a message asking for you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='鐵爐堡的術士拉戈·黑鉗在找你，你要立刻到他那裡向他報告。你可以在鐵爐堡的荒棄的洞穴裡找到他。' WHERE entry=768; /* Text0_0: You\'ve been summoned by Lago Blackwrench, warlock master of Ironforge. You\'d do yourself well to report to him immediately. You\'ll find him in the Forlorn Cavern district of the city. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你好，$R，我是薩納瑞恩·綠樹。' WHERE entry=769; /* Text0_0: Greetings $R, I am Tharnariun Treetender. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='如果你問我，那我要說，哥布林的科技更加先進。我們有工具，我們還有天賦!',Text0_1_loc5='如果你問我，那我要說，哥布林的科技更加先進。我們有工具，我們還有天賦!',Text1_0_loc5='要不是地精的狗屎運，他們就永遠不會贏!',Text1_1_loc5='要不是地精的狗屎運，他們就永遠不會贏!' WHERE entry=778; /* Text0_0: If you ask me, I think the goblins are a shoe in.  We have the tools, and we have the talent! */ /* Text0_1: If you ask me, I think the goblins are a shoe in.  We have the tools, and we have the talent! */ /* Text1_0: If it weren\'t for that cursed, gnomish luck, they\'d never win a race! */ /* Text1_1: If it weren\'t for that cursed, gnomish luck, they\'d never win a race! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc5='如果我是你，我就賭哥布林贏。壓其他車隊都是在浪費時間。',Text2_1_loc5='如果我是你，我就賭哥布林贏。壓其他車隊都是在浪費時間。',Text3_0_loc5='我已經把錢壓在哥布林身上了!如果你夠聰明的話也應該賭哥布林獲勝!',Text3_1_loc5='我已經把錢壓在哥布林身上了!如果你夠聰明的話也應該賭哥布林獲勝!' WHERE entry=778; /* Text2_0: If I were you, I\'d buy a goblin race voucher.  Rooting for the other team is a waste of time. */ /* Text2_1: If I were you, I\'d buy a goblin race voucher.  Rooting for the other team is a waste of time. */ /* Text3_0: My money\'s on the goblins!  And if you have any sense then yours is too! */ /* Text3_1: My money\'s on the goblins!  And if you have any sense then yours is too! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc5='我聽說下一場比賽的時候他們要把地精的車炸掉!不管是真是假，我會待在安全的地方。',Text4_1_loc5='我聽說下一場比賽的時候他們要把地精的車炸掉!不管是真是假，我會待在安全的地方。' WHERE entry=778; /* Text4_0: I heard they were going to try to blow up the gnome\'s car in the next race!  True or not, I\'d stand clear of their pit area. */ /* Text4_1: I heard they were going to try to blow up the gnome\'s car in the next race!  True or not, I\'d stand clear of their pit area. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='哦，你說的是強森?我聽說他躲起來了。',Text0_1_loc5='哦，你說的是強森?我聽說他躲起來了。',Text1_0_loc5='哈!提爾斯這段時間以來都在找他，但是他不想被找到。他是一隻小雞。',Text1_1_loc5='哈!提爾斯這段時間以來都在找他，但是他不想被找到。他是一隻小雞。' WHERE entry=779; /* Text0_0: Oh, you mean Johnson?  I heard he\'s in hiding. */ /* Text0_1: Oh, you mean Johnson?  I heard he\'s in hiding. */ /* Text1_0: Hah!  Tirth\'s been looking for him for days, but he doesn\'t want to be found.  He\'s chicken! */ /* Text1_1: Hah!  Tirth\'s been looking for him for days, but he doesn\'t want to be found.  He\'s chicken! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc5='你在尋找勇氣?哦，你沒聽到我的話，但是...或許你該問問塔里的科魯克萊德，他會告訴你...',Text2_1_loc5='你在尋找勇氣?哦，你沒聽到我的話，但是...或許你該問問塔里的科魯克萊德，他會告訴你...' WHERE entry=779; /* Text2_0: You looking for plucky?  Well, you didn\'t hear me say this, but... maybe if you ask Kronkrider up in the tower, he\'ll tell you... */ /* Text2_1: You looking for plucky?  Well, you didn\'t hear me say this, but... maybe if you ask Kronkrider up in the tower, he\'ll tell you... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='要不是哥布林的狗屎運，他們每次都會把車撞進山裡去!',Text0_1_loc5='要不是哥布林的狗屎運，他們每次都會把車撞進山裡去!',Text1_0_loc5='這種車賽是展現我們高新科技的大好機會!',Text1_1_loc5='這種車賽是展現我們高新科技的大好機會!' WHERE entry=780; /* Text0_0: If it weren\'t for the goblins\' inconceivable, dumb luck, they\'d crash their car during every race! */ /* Text0_1: If it weren\'t for the goblins\' inconceivable, dumb luck, they\'d crash their car during every race! */ /* Text1_0: These races are a great opportunity to show our ingenuity! */ /* Text1_1: These races are a great opportunity to show our ingenuity! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc5='我給我們的車裡安裝了新的矩陣式調節器，它可以使賽車的引擎轉速提高至少百分之十五!',Text2_1_loc5='我給我們的車裡安裝了新的矩陣式調節器，它可以使賽車的引擎轉速提高至少百分之十五!',Text3_0_loc5='我那兩歲的兒子設計的賽車都比那些可笑的哥布林造出來的破銅爛鐵跑得更快!',Text3_1_loc5='我那兩歲的兒子設計的賽車都比那些可笑的哥布林造出來的破銅爛鐵跑得更快!' WHERE entry=780; /* Text2_0: I installed a new device in our car\'s matrix regulometer.  That should increase its velocity quotient by a factor of no less than fifteen! */ /* Text2_1: I installed a new device in our car\'s matrix regulometer.  That should increase its velocity quotient by a factor of no less than fifteen! */ /* Text3_0: My son could design a faster car than that clunky goblin junk heap! */ /* Text3_1: My son could design a faster car than that clunky goblin junk heap! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc5='我的資料分析師認為這次我們會比上次的紀錄提高二十秒!',Text4_1_loc5='我的資料分析師認為這次我們會比上次的紀錄提高二十秒!' WHERE entry=780; /* Text4_0: My Gizmotic Almanacotron says that we should beat the goblins by twenty seconds more than we did last time! */ /* Text4_1: My Gizmotic Almanacotron says that we should beat the goblins by twenty seconds more than we did last time! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='這些天提爾斯和他的助手都變得怪怪的。',Text0_1_loc5='這些天提爾斯和他的助手都變得怪怪的。',Text1_0_loc5='強森?我認為他在附近的某個地方...',Text1_1_loc5='強森?我認為他在附近的某個地方...' WHERE entry=781; /* Text0_0: Tirth\'s not himself these days, and neither is his assistant. */ /* Text0_1: Tirth\'s not himself these days, and neither is his assistant. */ /* Text1_0: Johnson?  I think he\'s around here somewhere... */ /* Text1_1: Johnson?  I think he\'s around here somewhere... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc5='大膽的強森?我聽說塔頂的賽場主管，科魯克萊德，知道他在哪兒。',Text2_1_loc5='大膽的強森?我聽說塔頂的賽場主管，科魯克萊德，知道他在哪兒。' WHERE entry=781; /* Text2_0: Plucky?  I heard race master Kronkrider up on the the tower knows where he is. */ /* Text2_1: Plucky?  I heard race master Kronkrider up on the the tower knows where he is. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='終於!終於從這破牢房裡逃出來了!$b$b祈倫托將我從達拉然派到這個銀松森林裡來，要我調查阿魯高和他的亡靈僕從們的活動，可我們卻一點也不知道那個巫師已經完全失去了理智。$b$b我必須立刻把這個消息彙報上去!可在我離開之前，讓我先把庭院門上的魔法鎖給打開。$b$b既然你能擊敗雷希戈爾，或許也能從前面的層層埋伏中殺出一條血路...' WHERE entry=798; /* Text0_0: At last! I am finally free from this cell!$b$bThe Kirin Tor sent me from Dalaran to investigate Arugal\'s progress with the undead here in Silverpine Forest. Little did we know that the wizard had lost his grasp on sanity.$b$bI must report this mess at once! But before I leave, allow me to undo the magical lock on the courtyard door.$b$bYou defeated Rethilgore, perhaps you will survive what lies beyond.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='終於!終於有人把我從這破牢房裡給救出來了!$b$b高階執行官哈德瑞克大人派我們來這兒收集這座要塞裡的資訊，以便制定一個能永久消滅剷除阿魯高的計畫。$b$b但那個老不死的巫師還真有點能耐，我們很快就被他的魔法結界給發現了。我被抓來關在這裡，不過文森可就沒這麼走運了。$b$b我得馬上回去向哈德瑞克大人彙報。首先我會把庭院裡的鎖給你打開，或許你這麼強悍的$c能從前面的一大堆伏兵裡殺出一條血路...' WHERE entry=799; /* Text0_0: At last! Someone to free me from this cell!$b$bHigh Executor Hadrec sent us to gather information on the Keep so that a plan could be formulated to overthrow Arugal once and for all.$b$bBut the old wizard has many tricks up his sleeve and we were detected by a magical ward. I was thrown in this prison. Vincent was not so lucky.$b$bI must return to Hadrec to debrief him at once. But first I will pick the lock to the courtyard door for you. Perhaps you can try your luck against the foes that lurk beyond. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='我以前曾經追尋過暮光之錘的道路。為了找到復活上古諸神的方法，我隻身深入這座巢穴，想要找到從那個該死的惡魔阿庫麥爾身上抽取能量的方法。$B$B在看到無數無辜人白白地犧牲之後，我慢慢恢復了理智。$B$B我被困住了一段時間，但是現在我自由了!不幸的是，這裡離我的家鄉卡茲莫丹太遠了!$B$B勇敢的冒險者，我現在可以將你傳送至一個特別的地方，然後回來幹掉阿庫麥爾。如果你願意的話，我現在就送你到達納蘇斯去。' WHERE entry=818; /* Text0_0: I once followed the ways of the Twilight\'s Hammer. Obsessed with reviving the Old Gods, I journeyed deep into this lair to try to draw power from the cursed beast, Aku\'mai!$b$bAfter witnessing the sacrifice of countless innocents, I came to my senses.$b$bI was trapped but now I am free! But so far from my homeland of Khaz Modan!$b$bBrave adventurer, I offer you passage to a very special land in return for slaying Aku\'mai. If you wish, I can port you to the city of Darnassus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='歡迎來到我的旅店，疲累的旅人。我能為你做點什麼嗎?',Text0_1_loc5='歡迎來到我的旅店，疲累的旅人。我能為你做點什麼嗎?' WHERE entry=820; /* Text0_0: Welcome to my Inn, weary traveler. What can I do for you? */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to my Inn, weary traveler. What can I do for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='放鬆一下自己疲倦的身心。',Text0_1_loc5='放鬆一下自己疲倦的身心。' WHERE entry=821; /* Text0_0: Rest your weary bones for a spell. */ /* Text0_1: Rest your weary bones for a spell. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='我們一直歡迎你的到來，就像我們歡迎平原上吹過的風。',Text0_1_loc5='我們一直歡迎你的到來，就像我們歡迎平原上吹過的風。' WHERE entry=822; /* Text0_0: As the wind on the plains, you are always welcome here. */ /* Text0_1: As the wind on the plains, you are always welcome here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='滿上一杯啤酒，拉一張凳子過來坐坐。我們要暢飲一番，同時還要分享我們的故事。',Text0_1_loc5='滿上一杯啤酒，拉一張凳子過來坐坐。我們要暢飲一番，同時還要分享我們的故事。' WHERE entry=823; /* Text0_0: Fill yer tankard and pull up a chair. We\'ve stories to tell and kegs to empty. */ /* Text0_1: Fill yer tankard and pull up a chair. We\'ve stories to tell and kegs to empty. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你看起來很疲憊。在我們的屋裡休息一會兒吧，讓伊露恩引領你進入甜美的夢鄉。',Text0_1_loc5='你看起來很疲憊。在我們的屋裡休息一會兒吧，讓伊露恩引領你進入甜美的夢鄉。' WHERE entry=824; /* Text0_0: Your body looks worn and your spirit weary. Rest yourself beneath our roof and allow Elune to guide your dreams. */ /* Text0_1: Your body looks worn and your spirit weary. Rest yourself beneath our roof and allow Elune to guide your dreams. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='請進，請進!不要坐得離火爐太近。它今天還沒爆炸，但是為了安全起見，我想你還是坐在別的地方比較好。',Text0_1_loc5='請進，請進!不要坐得離火爐太近。它今天還沒爆炸，但是為了安全起見，我想你還是坐在別的地方比較好。' WHERE entry=825; /* Text0_0: Come in, come in. Just don\'t sit too close to the stove. It hasn\'t exploded yet today, but just to be safe I think you should sit elsewhere. */ /* Text0_1: Come in, come in. Just don\'t sit too close to the stove. It hasn\'t exploded yet today, but just to be safe I think you should sit elsewhere. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='看看誰來了...有什麼我能幫忙的嗎，$c?',Text0_1_loc5='看看誰來了...有什麼我能幫忙的嗎，$c?' WHERE entry=878; /* Text0_0: Well, well... look what the cat brung in... and how can I help you, $c? */ /* Text0_1: Well, well... look what the cat brung in... and how can I help you, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你可以在英雄谷東北邊的那個城堡平臺上找到獅鷲獸管理員。',Text0_1_loc5='你可以在英雄谷東北邊的那個城堡平臺上找到獅鷲獸管理員。',Text1_0_loc5='啊，你在找杜加爾·朗德瑞克。他那裡有卡茲莫丹飛得最快的獅鷲獸!你可以在貿易區的外牆上找到他。',Text1_1_loc5='啊，你在找杜加爾·朗德瑞克。他那裡有卡茲莫丹飛得最快的獅鷲獸!你可以在貿易區的外牆上找到他。' WHERE entry=879; /* Text0_0: You can find the gryphon master on the northeast rampart overlooking the Valley of Heroes. */ /* Text0_1: You can find the gryphon master on the northeast rampart overlooking the Valley of Heroes. */ /* Text1_0: Ahhh, you are looking for Dungar Longdrink. He has some of the fastest gryphons this side of Khaz Modan! You can find him up on the ramparts in the Trade District. */ /* Text1_1: Ahhh, you are looking for Dungar Longdrink. He has some of the fastest gryphons this side of Khaz Modan! You can find him up on the ramparts in the Trade District. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc5='你需要租用一隻獅鷲獸進行飛行，是嗎?杜加爾就在貿易區的城牆上，他那裡有很多獅鷲獸，記著飛行的時候要抓緊哦!',Text2_1_loc5='你需要租用一隻獅鷲獸進行飛行，是嗎?杜加爾就在貿易區的城牆上，他那裡有很多獅鷲獸，記著飛行的時候要抓緊哦!' WHERE entry=879; /* Text2_0: Lookin\' to take a gryphon ride, eh? Dungar keeps his birds up on the rampart in the Trade District. Just remember to hold on tight! */ /* Text2_1: Lookin\' to take a gryphon ride, eh? Dungar keeps his birds up on the rampart in the Trade District. Just remember to hold on tight! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你可以在貿易區的暴風城訪客中心裡找到奧德文·拉弗林。',Text0_1_loc5='你可以在貿易區的暴風城訪客中心裡找到奧德文·拉弗林。' WHERE entry=882; /* Text0_0: You can find Aldwin Laughlin at the Stormwind Visitor\'s Center in the Trade District. */ /* Text0_1: You can find Aldwin Laughlin at the Stormwind Visitor\'s Center in the Trade District. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc5='哈，你要找的是暴風城訪客中心。從英雄谷走到貿易區後左手邊的第一座建築就是了。',Text2_1_loc5='哈，你要找的是暴風城訪客中心。從英雄谷走到貿易區後左手邊的第一座建築就是了。' WHERE entry=882; /* Text2_0: Ahhh, Stormwind Visitor\'s Center is what you are looking for then. It\'s the first building on the left as you walk through the front gates from the Valley of Heroes. */ /* Text2_1: Ahhh, Stormwind Visitor\'s Center is what you are looking for then. It\'s the first building on the left as you walk through the front gates from the Valley of Heroes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你要尋找哪種職業的訓練師?',Text0_1_loc5='你要尋找哪種職業的訓練師?' WHERE entry=898; /* Text0_0: Which class trainer are you looking for? */ /* Text0_1: Which class trainer are you looking for? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='法師們都聚集在法師區的巫師聖所裡，那裡有一座高塔。和它相比，我們的兵營就好像是一座農舍。',Text0_1_loc5='法師們都聚集在法師區的巫師聖所裡，那裡有一座高塔。和它相比，我們的兵營就好像是一座農舍。',Text1_0_loc5='哦，你正在學習魔法?那沒有什麼地方會比法師區的巫師聖所更好了。',Text1_1_loc5='哦，你正在學習魔法?那沒有什麼地方會比法師區的巫師聖所更好了。' WHERE entry=899; /* Text0_0: The magi congregate in the Wizard\'s Sanctum in the Mage Quarter. Quite a tower they have there. Makes our barracks look like peasant hovels. */ /* Text0_1: The magi congregate in the Wizard\'s Sanctum in the Mage Quarter. Quite a tower they have there. Makes our barracks look like peasant hovels. */ /* Text1_0: Oh, looking for some arcane enlightenment are you? No place better then then Wizard\'s Sanctum in the Mage Quarter. */ /* Text1_1: Oh, looking for some arcane enlightenment are you? No place better then then Wizard\'s Sanctum in the Mage Quarter. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc5='聽起來你得去跟瑪姬諾·仲馬談談!你可以在法師區的巫師聖所找到他。當然，那些法師總是來去無蹤...',Text2_1_loc5='聽起來你得去跟瑪姬諾·仲馬談談!你可以在法師區的巫師聖所找到他。當然，那些法師總是來去無蹤...' WHERE entry=899; /* Text2_0: Sounds like you want to talk to Maginor Dumas! You can usually find him in the Wizard\'s Sanctum in the Mage Quarter. Course, you never know when or where those magi will portal off to. */ /* Text2_1: Sounds like you want to talk to Maginor Dumas! You can usually find him in the Wizard\'s Sanctum in the Mage Quarter. Course, you never know when or where those magi will portal off to. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你應該和奧斯伯談談。暴風城沒有比他更擅長潛行藝術了，那傢伙就在舊城區裡。',Text0_1_loc5='你應該和奧斯伯談談。暴風城沒有比他更擅長潛行藝術了，那傢伙就在舊城區裡。',Text1_0_loc5='哎，盜賊只會影響我們在暴風城的工作。我真希望能把奧斯伯和馬迪亞斯直接送到暴風城監獄去。',Text1_1_loc5='哎，盜賊只會影響我們在暴風城的工作。我真希望能把奧斯伯和馬迪亞斯直接送到暴風城監獄去。' WHERE entry=900; /* Text0_0: You want to talk to Osborne then. No finer teacher of the stealth arts than him in Stormwind. Look for him over in Old Town. */ /* Text0_1: You want to talk to Osborne then. No finer teacher of the stealth arts than him in Stormwind. Look for him over in Old Town. */ /* Text1_0: Bah, rogues have done nothing but make our job here in Stormwind harder. I wish I could drag both Osborne and Mathias both out of Old Town and right to the Stockade. */ /* Text1_1: Bah, rogues have done nothing but make our job here in Stormwind harder. I wish I could drag both Osborne and Mathias both out of Old Town and right to the Stockade. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='戰士們一般都在豬和哨聲旅店或者在舊城區的兵營裡出沒。但我建議你還是到旅店去找找比較好。',Text0_1_loc5='戰士們一般都在豬和哨聲旅店或者在舊城區的兵營裡出沒。但我建議你還是到旅店去找找比較好。',Text1_0_loc5='想要接受訓練?我可以把你訓練成暴風城最好的戰士，但是守衛是不能這麼做的。我想你得去兵營或者豬和哨聲旅店，找些合適的人來對你進行訓練。',Text1_1_loc5='想要接受訓練?我可以把你訓練成暴風城最好的戰士，但是守衛是不能這麼做的。我想你得去兵營或者豬和哨聲旅店，找些合適的人來對你進行訓練。' WHERE entry=901; /* Text0_0: Warriors can usually be found either at the Pig and Whistle Tavern or the Barracks in Old Town. Tell ya though, the tavern is probably a better place to look. */ /* Text0_1: Warriors can usually be found either at the Pig and Whistle Tavern or the Barracks in Old Town. Tell ya though, the tavern is probably a better place to look. */ /* Text1_0: Looking for some training, eh? I could train you better then anyone in Stormwind but the guard prohibits it. I guess you will have to settle for one of those has beens hanging out around the Barracks or at the Pig and Whistle Tavern in Old Town. */ /* Text1_1: Looking for some training, eh? I could train you better then anyone in Stormwind but the guard prohibits it. I guess you will have to settle for one of those has beens hanging out around the Barracks or at the Pig and Whistle Tavern in Old Town. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc5='去兵營或者豬和哨聲旅店逛逛吧。如果你去旅店的話，別忘了嘗嘗那裡的好酒，那些酒絕對能讓矮人的酒相形見絀。',Text2_1_loc5='去兵營或者豬和哨聲旅店逛逛吧。如果你去旅店的話，別忘了嘗嘗那裡的好酒，那些酒絕對能讓矮人的酒相形見絀。' WHERE entry=901; /* Text2_0: Check around Old Town at the Barracks or the Pig and Whistle Tavern. If you go to the tavern, be sure to sample some of the fine brews. Puts the dwarven ales to shame, I tell ya. */ /* Text2_1: Check around Old Town at the Barracks or the Pig and Whistle Tavern. If you go to the tavern, be sure to sample some of the fine brews. Puts the dwarven ales to shame, I tell ya. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你可以在花園區的月井旁邊找到塞瑞德蘭或者瑪爾德利恩。到法師區的北邊，教堂廣場的西邊就可以找到花園區了。',Text0_1_loc5='你可以在花園區的月井旁邊找到塞瑞德蘭或者瑪爾德利恩。到法師區的北邊，教堂廣場的西邊就可以找到花園區了。',Text1_0_loc5='如果你要尋找德魯伊訓練師，那就去花園區。塞瑞德蘭或者瑪爾德利恩一般都在那裡的月井旁邊。',Text1_1_loc5='如果你要尋找德魯伊訓練師，那就去花園區。塞瑞德蘭或者瑪爾德利恩一般都在那裡的月井旁邊。' WHERE entry=902; /* Text0_0: Well, you can find Theridan or Maldryn by the moonwell in the Park.  Just head to the western area of Stormwind, north of the Mage District, but west of the Cathedral Square. */ /* Text0_1: Well, you can find Theridan or Maldryn by the moonwell in the Park.  Just head to the western area of Stormwind, north of the Mage District, but west of the Cathedral Square. */ /* Text1_0: The Park is where you want to go if you are looking for druid trainers. Theridan and Maldryn can usually be found by the moonwell in the center of the district. */ /* Text1_1: The Park is where you want to go if you are looking for druid trainers. Theridan and Maldryn can usually be found by the moonwell in the center of the district. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc5='我們都是大自然的孩子，所以你到花園區的月井那邊去吧。',Text2_1_loc5='我們都是大自然的孩子，所以你到花園區的月井那邊去吧。' WHERE entry=902; /* Text2_0: A child of nature are we? Then you need look no further then the moonwell in the Park. */ /* Text2_1: A child of nature are we? Then you need look no further then the moonwell in the Park. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='教堂廣場的聖光大教堂是暴風城神職人員的住所，你可以在那裡找到高階牧師勞瑞娜。',Text0_1_loc5='教堂廣場的聖光大教堂是暴風城神職人員的住所，你可以在那裡找到高階牧師勞瑞娜。',Text1_0_loc5='勞瑞娜是暴風城的高階牧師，你可以在教堂廣場上的光明大教堂裡找到她。',Text1_1_loc5='勞瑞娜是暴風城的高階牧師，你可以在教堂廣場上的光明大教堂裡找到她。' WHERE entry=903; /* Text0_0: The Cathedral of Light in Cathedral Square is home to the priests of Stormwind. There you will find High Priestess Laurena. */ /* Text0_1: The Cathedral of Light in Cathedral Square is home to the priests of Stormwind. There you will find High Priestess Laurena. */ /* Text1_0: Laurena is the High Priestess of Stormwind. You can find her in the Catheral of Light in Cathedral Square. */ /* Text1_1: Laurena is the High Priestess of Stormwind. You can find her in the Catheral of Light in Cathedral Square. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc5='我建議你去教堂廣場上的聖光大教堂裡找一找。',Text2_1_loc5='我建議你去教堂廣場上的聖光大教堂裡找一找。' WHERE entry=903; /* Text2_0: I would suggest looking in the Cathedral of Light in Cathedral Square. */ /* Text2_1: I would suggest looking in the Cathedral of Light in Cathedral Square. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='如果你想變成強大的聖騎士，那麼格雷森·破影者領主是你最好的導師。你可以在教堂廣場上的聖光大教堂中找到他。',Text0_1_loc5='如果你想變成強大的聖騎士，那麼格雷森·破影者領主是你最好的導師。你可以在教堂廣場上的聖光大教堂中找到他。' WHERE entry=904; /* Text0_0: If you are looking to become a mighty paladin, there is no better teacher then Lord Grayson Shadowbreaker. He can be found in the Cathedral of Light in Cathedral Square. */ /* Text0_1: If you are looking to become a mighty paladin, there is no better teacher then Lord Grayson Shadowbreaker. He can be found in the Cathedral of Light in Cathedral Square. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='托爾芬·石盾從鐵爐堡而來，讓我們見識到了什麼叫真正的狩獵藝術。如果你不介意被煙燻得淚流滿面，就到矮人區去找他吧。他的屋子就在那個區域的東北部。',Text0_1_loc5='托爾芬·石盾從鐵爐堡而來，讓我們見識到了什麼叫真正的狩獵藝術。如果你不介意被煙燻得淚流滿面，就到矮人區去找他吧。他的屋子就在那個區域的東北部。' WHERE entry=905; /* Text0_0: Thorfin Stoneshield came to us all the way from Ironforge to bring us his expertise in hunting.  If you don\'t mind breathing the smoke filled air of the Dwarven District then you\'ll find him at his house in the northeast area of the district. */ /* Text0_1: Thorfin Stoneshield came to us all the way from Ironforge to bring us his expertise in hunting.  If you don\'t mind breathing the smoke filled air of the Dwarven District then you\'ll find him at his house in the northeast area of the district. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='是什麼把你帶到這個地方的，$n?',Text0_1_loc5='是什麼把你帶到這個地方的，$n?' WHERE entry=907; /* Text0_0: What brings you to this part of the world, $n? */ /* Text0_1: What brings you to this part of the world, $n? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你想找哪種專業技能訓練師?',Text0_1_loc5='你想找哪種專業技能訓練師?' WHERE entry=918; /* Text0_0: Which profession trainer are you looking for? */ /* Text0_1: Which profession trainer are you looking for? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='如果你要學習鍊金術，暴風城只有一個地方值得你去...那就是鍊金材料店。你可以沿著法師區的週邊找到這家店鋪。',Text0_1_loc5='如果你要學習鍊金術，暴風城只有一個地方值得你去...那就是鍊金材料店。你可以沿著法師區的週邊找到這家店鋪。',Text1_0_loc5='他在法師區，那兒有一間名叫鍊金材料店的小商店。你會在前往法師區的沿途看到各種各樣奇怪的商店，但是如果你沿著週邊走的話，你一定會找到它的。',Text1_1_loc5='他在法師區，那兒有一間名叫鍊金材料店的小商店。你會在前往法師區的沿途看到各種各樣奇怪的商店，但是如果你沿著週邊走的話，你一定會找到它的。' WHERE entry=919; /* Text0_0: If you need training in alchemy, there is only one place in Stormwind you need to go... Alchemy Needs. You can find it in the Mage Quarter along the outer rim of shops. */ /* Text0_1: If you need training in alchemy, there is only one place in Stormwind you need to go... Alchemy Needs. You can find it in the Mage Quarter along the outer rim of shops. */ /* Text1_0: Tucked away in the Mage Quarter, there is a little shop called Alchemy Needs.  You\'re bound to see all sort of strange shops on your way through the Mage Quarter, but if you stick to the outer rim you\'ll be sure to find it. */ /* Text1_1: Tucked away in the Mage Quarter, there is a little shop called Alchemy Needs.  You\'re bound to see all sort of strange shops on your way through the Mage Quarter, but if you stick to the outer rim you\'ll be sure to find it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你應該去找瑟魯姆·深爐談談，他是我見過的最好的矮人鐵匠。你可以在矮人區的中心地帶找到他。',Text0_1_loc5='你應該去找瑟魯姆·深爐談談，他是我見過的最好的矮人鐵匠。你可以在矮人區的中心地帶找到他。',Text1_0_loc5='你說你不能在這兒聞到矮人鍛爐的煙味?哦，如果你想學習鍛造的話就該找瑟魯姆·深爐。他就在大教堂廣場北邊的矮人區。',Text1_1_loc5='你說你不能在這兒聞到矮人鍛爐的煙味?哦，如果你想學習鍛造的話就該找瑟魯姆·深爐。他就在大教堂廣場北邊的矮人區。' WHERE entry=920; /* Text0_0: Therum Deepforge is the dwarf you want to talk to. One of the finest blacksmiths around if you ask me. You can find him in the heart of the Dwarven District. */ /* Text0_1: Therum Deepforge is the dwarf you want to talk to. One of the finest blacksmiths around if you ask me. You can find him in the heart of the Dwarven District. */ /* Text1_0: You mean you can\'t smell the smoke of the Dwarven forges from here?  Well, you will be looking for Therum Deepforge if you want to learn blacksmithing.  He\'s over in the Dwarven District which is just north of the Cathedral Square. */ /* Text1_1: You mean you can\'t smell the smoke of the Dwarven forges from here?  Well, you will be looking for Therum Deepforge if you want to learn blacksmithing.  He\'s over in the Dwarven District which is just north of the Cathedral Square. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='暴風城有一個天才地精名叫利廉姆·火軸，他是這裡最好的工程學訓練師。你可以在矮人區的後面找到他。',Text0_1_loc5='暴風城有一個天才地精名叫利廉姆·火軸，他是這裡最好的工程學訓練師。你可以在矮人區的後面找到他。' WHERE entry=922; /* Text0_0: Stormwind\'s resident engineer trainer is an ingenious gnome by the name of Lilliam Sparkspindle. He can be found in the back of the Dwarven District. */ /* Text0_1: Stormwind\'s resident engineer trainer is an ingenious gnome by the name of Lilliam Sparkspindle. He can be found in the back of the Dwarven District. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你可以在法師區的鍊金材料店外面找到塔尼莎。',Text0_1_loc5='你可以在法師區的鍊金材料店外面找到塔尼莎。',Text1_0_loc5='與自然的交流溝通是其他任何事情都無可比擬的...至少夜精靈是這麼告訴我的。我並不擅長跟花草樹木交談，但是我想塔尼莎能幫助你。她居住在法師區外側的鍊金材料店。',Text1_1_loc5='與自然的交流溝通是其他任何事情都無可比擬的...至少夜精靈是這麼告訴我的。我並不擅長跟花草樹木交談，但是我想塔尼莎能幫助你。她居住在法師區外側的鍊金材料店。' WHERE entry=924; /* Text0_0: You can find Tannysa standing outside Alchemy Needs in the Mage Quarter. */ /* Text0_1: You can find Tannysa standing outside Alchemy Needs in the Mage Quarter. */ /* Text1_0: There\'s nothing quite like communing with nature... or at least that\'s what the night elves tell me.  I\'m not much for talking to flowers and trees, but I\'m sure Tannysa could help you out.  She\'s over in the Mage Quarter outside of Alchemy Needs. */ /* Text1_1: There\'s nothing quite like communing with nature... or at least that\'s what the night elves tell me.  I\'m not much for talking to flowers and trees, but I\'m sure Tannysa could help you out.  She\'s over in the Mage Quarter outside of Alchemy Needs. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你想要學習製皮?西蒙·坦納爾可以教你。你可以在舊城區的「護體皮甲」店裡找到他。',Text0_1_loc5='你想要學習製皮?西蒙·坦納爾可以教你。你可以在舊城區的「護體皮甲」店裡找到他。',Text1_0_loc5='你想要穿皮甲對嗎?聽起來你該與舊城區的西蒙·坦納爾談談。他在那兒開了一家叫做護體皮甲的商店。',Text1_1_loc5='你想要穿皮甲對嗎?聽起來你該與舊城區的西蒙·坦納爾談談。他在那兒開了一家叫做護體皮甲的商店。' WHERE entry=925; /* Text0_0: Want to learn leatherworking, eh? Simon Tanner would be able to teach you. He can be found in Old Town at the Protective Hide. */ /* Text0_1: Want to learn leatherworking, eh? Simon Tanner would be able to teach you. He can be found in Old Town at the Protective Hide. */ /* Text1_0: You\'re into leather, eh?  Sounds like you should talk to Simon Tanner over in Old Town.  He runs a shop there called the Protective Hide. */ /* Text1_1: You\'re into leather, eh?  Sounds like you should talk to Simon Tanner over in Old Town.  He runs a shop there called the Protective Hide. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你可以去找吉爾曼·石手談談。我知道他在矮人區有一棟房子，但我不知道確切的地方。如果我是你的話，我就會去那邊看看。',Text0_1_loc5='你可以去找吉爾曼·石手談談。我知道他在矮人區有一棟房子，但我不知道確切的地方。如果我是你的話，我就會去那邊看看。',Text1_0_loc5='讓矮人從鐵爐堡指派一名採礦專家來教教我們吧。使用鋤頭打碎岩石有多困難?嗯，只要他在這兒，你就只管問他好了。他名叫吉爾曼，居住在矮人區。',Text1_1_loc5='讓矮人從鐵爐堡指派一名採礦專家來教教我們吧。使用鋤頭打碎岩石有多困難?嗯，只要他在這兒，你就只管問他好了。他名叫吉爾曼，居住在矮人區。' WHERE entry=927; /* Text0_0: Gelman Stonehand would be the one to talk to. I think he has a house over in the Dwarven District but I can\'t remember exactly. I would check over there. */ /* Text0_1: Gelman Stonehand would be the one to talk to. I think he has a house over in the Dwarven District but I can\'t remember exactly. I would check over there. */ /* Text1_0: Leave it to the dwarves to send a mining specialist from Ironforge to tell us how to mine.  How hard is it to take a pick and chip away at some rock?  Well, since he\'s here, he\'s probably the one you should see anyhow.  His name is Gelman and he resides over in the Dwarven District. */ /* Text1_1: Leave it to the dwarves to send a mining specialist from Ironforge to tell us how to mine.  How hard is it to take a pick and chip away at some rock?  Well, since he\'s here, he\'s probably the one you should see anyhow.  His name is Gelman and he resides over in the Dwarven District. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='如果你要去學剝皮術，可以到舊城區的「護體皮甲」店裡看看。',Text0_1_loc5='如果你要去學剝皮術，可以到舊城區的「護體皮甲」店裡看看。' WHERE entry=928; /* Text0_0: You are gonna want to head over to Old Town and drop by the Protective Hide if you are lookin\' to learn skinning. */ /* Text0_1: You are gonna want to head over to Old Town and drop by the Protective Hide if you are lookin\' to learn skinning. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='鄧肯雇傭了暴風城最好的裁縫，喬吉奧·波利羅。他的店就坐落在法師區裡。',Text0_1_loc5='鄧肯雇傭了暴風城最好的裁縫，喬吉奧·波利羅。他的店就坐落在法師區裡。',Text1_0_loc5='一個裁縫是嗎?哦，如果你在這兒待的時間夠長你最後就會聽到關於喬吉奧·波利羅的談論。他現在已經領導潮流幾個月了。如果你希望跟他學習，你能在法師區的外圈找到他。',Text1_1_loc5='一個裁縫是嗎?哦，如果你在這兒待的時間夠長你最後就會聽到關於喬吉奧·波利羅的談論。他現在已經領導潮流幾個月了。如果你希望跟他學習，你能在法師區的外圈找到他。' WHERE entry=929; /* Text0_0: Duncan\'s Textiles employs one of the finest tailors in Stormwind, Georgio Bolero. Look for the shop over in the Mage Quarter. */ /* Text0_1: Duncan\'s Textiles employs one of the finest tailors in Stormwind, Georgio Bolero. Look for the shop over in the Mage Quarter. */ /* Text1_0: A tailor is it?  Well, if you hang out here long enough you\'ll eventually hear word of mouth about Georgio Bolero.  He\'s been setting the trends for some months now.  If you wish to learn from him, you can find him over in the Mage Quarter in the outer rim. */ /* Text1_1: A tailor is it?  Well, if you hang out here long enough you\'ll eventually hear word of mouth about Georgio Bolero.  He\'s been setting the trends for some months now.  If you wish to learn from him, you can find him over in the Mage Quarter in the outer rim. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='強森不想讓提爾斯知道他還在閃光平原，所以他把自己變成了一隻小雞!$B$B如果你找到強森，就向他招招手。說不定他會跑過來的。' WHERE entry=930; /* Text0_0: Plucky doesn\'t want Tirth to know he\'s still in the Shimmering Flats, so he turned himself into a chicken!$B$BIf you find Plucky, beckon him to you.  Maybe he\'ll come out of hiding. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='我希望你已經準備好了。' WHERE entry=931; /* Text0_0: I hope yer ready to work. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='歡迎來觀看賽車!希望你喜歡這裡，但請記得不要把錢都下注在同一個地方!',Text0_1_loc5='歡迎來觀看賽車!希望你喜歡這裡，但請記得不要把錢都下注在同一個地方!',Text1_0_loc5='你好，$c!歡迎來閃光平原觀看賽車!',Text1_1_loc5='你好，$c!歡迎來閃光平原觀看賽車!' WHERE entry=932; /* Text0_0: Welcome to the races!  Enjoy your stay, and don\'t bet all your money in one place! */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to the races!  Enjoy your stay, and don\'t bet all your money in one place! */ /* Text1_0: Hello, $c!  Welcome to the races at the Shimmering Flats! */ /* Text1_1: Hello, $c!  Welcome to the races at the Shimmering Flats! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc5='哪個車隊的賽車最快?天知道?!?',Text2_1_loc5='哪個車隊的賽車最快?天知道?!?',Text3_0_loc5='哥布林的賽車馬力強勁，但地精的賽車也有不少獨到之處...',Text3_1_loc5='哥布林的賽車馬力強勁，但地精的賽車也有不少獨到之處...' WHERE entry=932; /* Text2_0: Who has the fastest car?  Who knows?!? */ /* Text2_1: Who has the fastest car?  Who knows?!? */ /* Text3_0: The goblin racer packs a lot of punch, but the gnomes hid a trick or two in their car... */ /* Text3_1: The goblin racer packs a lot of punch, but the gnomes hid a trick or two in their car... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你需要幫助嗎?',Text0_1_loc5='你需要幫助嗎?' WHERE entry=933; /* Text0_0: What do you need directions to? */ /* Text0_1: What do you need directions to? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='如果我們要成為這塊新地區的主人，那麼我們就必須要找個地方好好休息。把你的斧頭放在火邊，讓大家分享你英勇戰鬥的故事吧。',Text0_1_loc5='如果我們要成為這塊新地區的主人，那麼我們就必須要找個地方好好休息。把你的斧頭放在火邊，讓大家分享你英勇戰鬥的故事吧。' WHERE entry=938; /* Text0_0: If we are to make these new lands ours then we must have places to rest our battle weary bodies. Lay your axe by the fire and share the stories of your mighty battles. */ /* Text0_1: If we are to make these new lands ours then we must have places to rest our battle weary bodies. Lay your axe by the fire and share the stories of your mighty battles. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='魯坎·考迪爾在監獄附近的運河邊上有一家小店。我相信他可以教你附魔的技巧。',Text0_1_loc5='魯坎·考迪爾在監獄附近的運河邊上有一家小店。我相信他可以教你附魔的技巧。',Text1_0_loc5='啊，你是在找魯坎·考迪爾。他在魔法區外開了一家商店，你前往監獄時會經過那兒的。',Text1_1_loc5='啊，你是在找魯坎·考迪爾。他在魔法區外開了一家商店，你前往監獄時會經過那兒的。' WHERE entry=941; /* Text0_0: Lucan Cordell has a small shop on the canal by the Stockade. I am sure he will be able to teach you the art of enchanting. */ /* Text0_1: Lucan Cordell has a small shop on the canal by the Stockade. I am sure he will be able to teach you the art of enchanting. */ /* Text1_0: Ah, you\'re looking for Lucan Cordell.  He runs a shop on the outside of the Magic Quarter on your way to the Stockade. */ /* Text1_1: Ah, you\'re looking for Lucan Cordell.  He runs a shop on the outside of the Magic Quarter on your way to the Stockade. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='我獨自走在路上，為了捍衛榮譽和清除這片大陸上的敵人而戰。$B$B我能為你做什麼，$n?' WHERE entry=942; /* Text0_0: I walk this road alone, seeking ways to defend my honor and rid this land of our enemies.$B$BWhat can I do for you, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='是的，我見過你要找的薩滿。上次我見到她的時候，她正往西邊去。她隱居在剃鬃部族上方的小山上。如果你夠聰明的話，就可以找到一條通往小屋的山路，就在北邊不遠的地方。那條路可以讓你避開野豬人，直接找到她。' WHERE entry=943; /* Text0_0: Yes, I have seen the shaman you seek. Last I saw her, she was to the west of here. She hides in the hills above the Razormane tribe. If you\'re clever, you\'ll be able to find a path to her hut in the hills. It is not too far north of here. That path should allow you to find her without fighting through the quilboar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='無論索爾是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都將延續下去。' WHERE entry=1038; /* Text0_0: The Order of the Shattered Hand existed before Thrall and shall exist after Thrall. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='這台機器開始運轉了。' WHERE entry=1041; /* Text0_0: The machine comes alive at your touch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='他給你蜂蜜酒$b$b他給你啤酒$b$b他總是過著快樂的生活$b$b這麼多年他為我們每個人都服務過$b我們叫他微笑的吉姆。' WHERE entry=1058; /* Text0_0: He\'ll bring you mead$bHe\'ll bring you beer$bA grinning face from ear to ear$bHe\'s served us all from year to year$bWe call him Smiling Jim. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='這是一種非常奇怪的植物，你從未在泰達希爾的其他地方見過。' WHERE entry=1059; /* Text0_0: This is an exotic sample of flora, unseen in other parts of Teldrassil. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='這個植物矗立在泰達希爾的普通植物之間，散發著奇異的紫色光芒。' WHERE entry=1060; /* Text0_0: This plant stands out among the normal flora of Teldrassil, and emits a strange, purplish glow. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你好。我的職責在得到允許的情況下，根據艾澤拉斯的造物者對於土靈的分析，向來訪者提供相關的資訊。我隨時都可以與你分享這些資訊。' WHERE entry=1079; /* Text0_0: Salutations.  My function is to offer access to and, when permissible, insight into information regarding the Creators\' synthesis of the Earthen on the world designated as Azeroth.  I am ready to share this information with you now at your leisure. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='土靈是造物者設計的綜合產物，並作為艾澤拉斯開始的幾個種族之一。土靈被用於幫助造物者改善這個世界。$B$B他們是造物者在其他世界中設計的標準地下生物的改良形態。在最初的結構得以確定之後，這種原型產生了很多的變化。' WHERE entry=1080; /* Text0_0: The Earthen are a synthesized race engineered by the Creators, functioning as one of the seed races in the initial population of the world designated as Azeroth.  The Earthen were created to aid the Creators\' efforts in shaping the deep regions of this world.$B$BThey are a modification of the standard subterranean being matrix used on other worlds that the Creators have seeded.  The construction of this prototype race created various anomalies that were observed after initial synthesis. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='它是造物者在開創世界的時候創建的最早的一個物種。造物者所創建的每種生物都肩負了一定的使命。對於艾澤拉斯來說，必須改造原有的標準地下生物構造，使其適應地下深處的生活，土靈就是這種改造的產品。$B$B在土靈被創造出來之後，由於巨大的環境壓力，它們出現了許多事先無法預見的變化。' WHERE entry=1081; /* Text0_0: It is one of the synthesis matrices the Creators use when seeding a world.  Each synthesis matrix is used to achieve the Creators\' goals.  For Azeroth, a subterranean being matrix was modified to create a being with increased durability with an affinity for deep region shaping; the Earthen are the product of this modification.$B$BAfter the Earthen had been put into service for the Creators, unforeseen anomalies were discovered that affected their synthesis matrix due to high-stress environments. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='在正確回答這個問題之前，需要向你介紹更多關於土靈的背景資料。$B$B資料處理中。$B$B為了理解土靈的變化，首先要瞭解土靈的設計特徵。創世者的目的是要提高標準地下生物母體的存活性，因此他們把與整個世界相聯繫的彈性構造基礎整合在其中，土靈的出現正是為了達到這一目的。' WHERE entry=1082; /* Text0_0: Additional background information on the Earthen must be given to you before this question may be answered properly.$B$BProcessing.$B$BTo understand the anomalies of the Earthen, it is first important to understand what the Earthen represent in their design intent.  The Earthen represent the Creators\' attempt at improving the survivability paradigm of the standard subterranean being matrix.  This was done by incorporating a resilient foundation of construction inherent to the world into said matrix. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='所謂彈性構造基礎就是指用於種族合成的基本材料。造物者在創造土靈的時候放棄了以前創造世界時一直使用的基礎材料，轉而使用這種常見於艾澤拉斯的材料。$B$B通過對世界組成成分的分析，造物者認為可以合成一種加強型的生物，將它作為世界本質的縮影。造物者最終通過混合艾澤拉斯大陸上各種不同的石頭成分，最後組成了這樣一種生物的構造基礎。' WHERE entry=1083; /* Text0_0: It is the baseline material used in race synthesis.  A cross-section of Azeroth\'s crust was used as the foundation for the Earthen\'s synthesis rather than the typical biomass construction foundation used by the Creators.$B$BResearch on the world\'s composition led the Creators to theorize that an enhanced being could be synthesized that would epitomize the resiliency of this world\'s essence.  This was accomplished by choosing to use a blend of Azeroth\'s various stone core compounds as the foundation. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='簡單地說，事實確實如此。$B$B雖然土靈的外表看起來像是一個小型的人形生物，但它們包含了艾澤拉斯大陸上各種石頭的成分。它們在得到了力量和耐力最大化的同時也沒有犧牲敏銳的感覺。它們的皮膚和肌肉的設計使其幾乎完全免疫物理傷害，而且只需進行非常小的改造，土靈就可以展現出驚人的魔法抗性。' WHERE entry=1084; /* Text0_0: Simply stated, this is correct.$B$BThe Earthen\'s physical features are that of a smaller stature humanoid, though their composition is that of Azeroth\'s various stone core compounds.  Their design maximizes strength and stamina without sacrificing cognitive processing power.  Their skin and musculature are nearly impervious to physical damage, and with very minor modifications the Earthen display a remarkable resiliency to unwanted magical forces. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='以上這些內容是用來幫助你理解創世者的動機。他們創造出土靈這樣一個物種是為了在他們離開之後，土靈可以成為這個世界中的一個重要部分，並保障創世者在艾澤拉斯世界的宏大計畫得以繼續執行。$B$B創世者對於「土靈」這個名字十分滿意，因為它很好地體現了這個種族的基本特性。' WHERE entry=1085; /* Text0_0: It is integral to the assimilation of this data that it is understood that the Creators wanted to synthesize a race that would long be an integral part of this world\'s development cycle after they had departed.  This race would be instrumental in fulfilling the Creators\' long-term development objectives for Azeroth.  $B$BAs an ancillary note, the nomenclature "Earthen" was deemed apropos for the new race by the Creators, based on the Earthen\'s composition. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='土靈唯一的異常變化是在高壓環境下使用時容易使基質失序。$B$B附錄:原基質的設記是適合地底雕塑，因此從未進行高壓環境複製測試。$B$B這種失序直到土靈首度進入服務循環之後才被發現。造物者開始對土靈進行成體改造，而非將之召回並重新設計。' WHERE entry=1086; /* Text0_0: The Earthen\'s only anomaly in synthesis is the tendency for matrix destabilization while being utilized in high-stress environments.$B$BAddendum: deep earth sculpting was naturally suited to the new matrix design and thus never met the qualifications of duplicating a high-stress environment.$B$BDestabilization was not discovered until well into the Earthen\'s primary service cycle for the Creators.  The Creators began work on post-synthesis modification, rather than recall and re-synthesis. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='[當你問了這個問題之後，它明顯地停頓了一會兒]$B$B你需要的資訊無法在該資料庫中獲取。對此我表示歉意。$B$B你可以在資料更新之後再次查詢該資訊，或者從艾澤拉斯的其他資訊資料庫處獲得更多資訊。' WHERE entry=1087; /* Text0_0: [There is a noticeable pause after you ask this question.]$B$BThe information you request is not currently available in this repository\'s data cycling.  I sincerely apologize for this omission.$B$BPlease request this information after a data cycling update has been performed on this information repository.  You may also request this information from another information repository located on Azeroth. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='當土靈的合成母體不穩定的時候，產生了兩個變種。一號教程圖像正在初始化。$B$B第一類變種被稱為「穴居怪」。這個變種保留了土靈的力量和耐力，但是它的感知力量完全喪失。欲望和狡詐成為了穴居怪的本能。' WHERE entry=1088; /* Text0_0: There are two potential results when the Earthen\'s synthesis matrix destabilizes.  Initiating visual aid representation number one.$B$BThe first variant matrix is a degenerative product of synthesis, hereby designated with the common nomenclature of "Trogg".  This variant maintains strength and stamina comparable to the Earthen, but its cognitive processing power has been almost completely compromised.  Force of will and a strong sense of cunning are the only driving factors in the psyche of the trogg. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='抱歉，我無法將現有記錄資料按照時間順序進行排序。$B$B雖然穴居怪仍然包含了艾澤拉斯的各種石頭的核心成分，但是它們感知能力的喪失是造物者無法接受的。$B$B穴居怪可以進行單體繁殖。它們會把所有的東西當作食物，包括石頭，甚至是另外一個穴居怪。這樣的同類相殘是造物者極度反感的。' WHERE entry=1089; /* Text0_0: I am unable to process your chronological reference in comparison to the recording of this data, my apologies.$B$BThe trogg retains some composition of Azeroth\'s various stone core compounds, but the loss of cognitive power makes this variant unacceptable to the Creators.$B$BThe trogg procreates as per a standard biomass.  By default it consumes stone and anything else it can acquire, including other troggs.  Cannibalism is considered unacceptable by the Creators. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='二號教程圖像正在初始化。$B$B土靈母體的第二個變種和標準的地下生物母體相比較而言，保留了很多必要的元素。這個種族被稱作「矮人」。$B$B這個變種同樣保留了土靈的力量和耐力。在某些方面，矮人甚至超過了土靈母體所具有的感知能力。但是，矮人這個變種的身體結構中已經完全沒有了石質成分的蹤跡。' WHERE entry=1090; /* Text0_0: Initiating visual aid representation number two.$B$BThe second resultant variance of the Earthen matrix retains many desired elements when compared to the standard subterranean matrix.  The common nomenclature for this variant is "Dwarf".$B$BThis variant retains strength and stamina inherent to the Earthen.  In some cases, the dwarf even exceeds the cognitive powers of the Earthen\'s matrix.  The dwarf, however, retains none of the physical composition of Azeroth\'s various stone core compounds. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你的問題在資料庫中有相關聯接。$B$B矮人依然和艾澤拉斯的各種石頭有著密切的關係，但是由於土靈在高壓環境下的變異，矮人的結構與標準地下生物母體的結構保持了一致。$B$B因此，正如你所猜想的那樣，矮人確實是從母體中變異出來的。' WHERE entry=1091; /* Text0_0: The data stored in this repository does indeed correlate with your astute proclamation.$B$BThe dwarf maintains an affinity for the stone composition of Azeroth, but due to the high-stress environmental anomaly within the Earthen\'s synthesis matrix, the dwarf reverts to a default biomass composition as seen in the standard subterranean matrix.$B$BErgo, the dwarf variant does synthesize from the degeneration of the Earthen creation matrix, as you inferred with your query. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='抱歉，我無法將現有記錄資料按照時間順序進行排序。$B$B雖然矮人還是和艾澤拉斯的各種石頭有著某種聯繫，但是他們更多的是向普通的地下物種發展。矮人的生活習性和繁衍方式都和其他的標準生物完全一致。$B$B造物者認為矮人是一種可以接受的變種，可以讓其繼續發展下去。' WHERE entry=1092; /* Text0_0: I am unable to process your chronological reference in comparison to the recording of this data, my apologies.$B$BThough the dwarf maintains most of the Earthen\'s mental attunement to Azeroth\'s stone composition, the reversion back into living biomass remains the main degeneration of the matrix.  Dwarves eat and procreate through means typical to other standard biomasses.$B$BThe Creators view the dwarf as an acceptable variant, worthy of genesis in its own right. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='造物者就是...造物者。$B$B他們根據自己的設計來創造和改變這個世界。他們是這個世界出現的原因，他們是艾澤拉斯的創造者。' WHERE entry=1093; /* Text0_0: The Creators are... the Creators.$B$BThey are the beings that seeded and shaped this world by their own design.  They are the reason for this world\'s existence, as well as many other worlds.  They are the wellspring from which Azeroth flows. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='造物者也知道這個資料庫中彙集了大量的資訊。所以，如果你擁有諾甘農圓盤的話，便可以得到一份所有資訊的拷貝。$B$B請確認你現在沒有關於這方面資訊的問題了。當你找到諾甘農圓盤之後，可以隨時過來製作拷貝。' WHERE entry=1094; /* Text0_0: The Creators are cognizant of the magnitude of the information housed in this repository.  Subsequently, a portable copy of the data stored here will be made available to you once you are attuned with the Discs of Norgannon.$B$BPlease consider your cursory requirements for the assimilation of this knowledge to be complete.  At your leisure, access the Discs of Norgannon to begin synthesis of your discs. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='那麼說來你想要成為一名鐵匠?紮好圍裙，拿起鐵錘$g小夥子:小姑娘;，讓我們開始吧。' WHERE entry=1118; /* Text0_0: So ye want to be a Blacksmith eh? Grab an Apron and a hammer $g lad : lass;, let\'s see what ye\'ve got. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='$n，我已經許久沒有看見過有上好的護甲被鍛造出來了。我以前曾經在大鍛爐的格魯努斯·削鋼那裡接受過訓練。我相信如果你去他那裡的話，肯定可以學到很多東西。' WHERE entry=1119; /* Text0_0: I\'ve not seen finer armor made in many years $N. Not since I trained under Grumnus Steelshaper in the Great Forge. I bet he could teach ye things about makin armor that would spark yer interest. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='如果你想要找格魯努斯的話，那麼首先要到鐵爐堡去，然後去城市中心的大鍛爐，在那裡你就可以找到格魯努斯。' WHERE entry=1120; /* Text0_0: If ye want to find Grumnus, the first thing ye should do is head to Ironforge. Go to the very center of the city and look for the Great Forge, ye should find him there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='$n，你已經擁有了驚人的鍛造技能。我不得不承認你鍛造出的武器已經超過了我的水準。我所認識的水準高過你的鐵匠只有博古斯·鋼拳，我相信你可以從他那裡學到不少東西。' WHERE entry=1121; /* Text0_0: That\'s some impressive skill ye have there $N. The blades and hammers ye make surpass even my own, hard as that is to admit. Only person I ever met with skill even greater is Borgus Steelhand, I bet he could teach ye a thing or three. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你想要接受博古斯的訓練?當然，我可以告訴你在什麼地方能夠找到他。往西北方向穿過廣場，然後再順著西面的路走，在右手邊的第二座建築物中可以找到他。' WHERE entry=1122; /* Text0_0: Want to train with Borgus? Aye, I can tell ye where to find him. Head through the Square northwest of me forge, then take the western road. Ye\'ll find him in the second building on yer right. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='歡迎來到大鍛爐，$g小夥子:姑娘;。外面雖然非常寒冷，但是這裡確實熱火朝天。拿起錘子開工吧，讓我看看你到底有些什麼能耐!' WHERE entry=1127; /* Text0_0: Welcome to the Great Forge $g lad : lass;. It may be cold outside but we keep it nice and hot down \'ere. Grab a hammer, strike that anvil and show me ye\'ve got what it takes to be a Blacksmith of the Great Forge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='幹得好，$n，我敢在布魯克小店賭一杯酒，你做的東西的確正點。你應該去和米洛爾·怒斬談談，他會給你更多指引的。' WHERE entry=1128; /* Text0_0: Nice form $N, I bet a full mug at Bruuk\'s Corner that the function is just as solid. Ye know, ye might want to talk to Myolor Sunderfury. He\'ll set ya straight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='當然，我可以告訴你怎麼才能找到米洛爾。他就在大鍛爐的鐵砧旁邊工作。仔細聆聽他的教導吧，$g小夥子:小姑娘;，米洛爾絕對名不虛傳!' WHERE entry=1129; /* Text0_0: Course I can show ye where Myolor is. Right over there near the anvil of the Great Forge, that\'s where he does his work. Listen to his words well $g lad:lass;, Myolor is as skilled as they come. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='$n，你已經得到了我的認可，你是我這些年來帶過的最好的徒弟。如果你想要鑄造一把真正的武器，那麼你一定要去和米洛爾·怒斬談談。那個矮人能夠教你鑄造出一把真真正正的絕世好劍。' WHERE entry=1130; /* Text0_0: Ye have my approval $N, ye can forge blades better than any I\'ve trained in years. If ye want to make a real weapon though, ye need to talk with Myolor Sunderfury. That Dwarf will set ya on the right path. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你要找米洛爾?他就在那兒，你瞧，就在你身後!呃，好吧，也許在你前面!反正就在大鍛砧附近!' WHERE entry=1131; /* Text0_0: So, off to see Myolor, eh? He\'s right o\'er there... behind ye! Er, maybe in front of ye! Near the Great Anvil! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你真的那麼笨嗎?你鍛造出來的是什麼東西?那最多算得上是一把水果刀罷了。我可不想浪費時間訓練菜鳥。' WHERE entry=1133; /* Text0_0: What are ye daft? That\'s not a weapon, that\'s a dinner knife. I don\'t train amateurs. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你打擾我就是為了這個?你穿得真是跟垃圾一樣，你還不如背隻死兔子到食人妖的洞裡去跑一圈!' WHERE entry=1135; /* Text0_0: Ye bothered me for that? Ye\'d be better off strapping a dead rabbit to yer back and running through a Troll\'s den than wearing that piece of garbage. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='$n，這真是你做的嗎?真是一件精美的作品。我會繼續訓練你的，相信總有一天你可以達到皇家鑄甲匠的水準。' WHERE entry=1136; /* Text0_0: $N, was it? That is a mighty fine piece of work ye have there. I\'ll take ye on, train ye how to make armor fit fer King Magni himself. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='大約五個月之前，風險投資公司荊棘谷分公司從藏寶海灣的一個名叫克蘭克·菲茲巴布的神秘商人那裡買了一瓶特別的毒藥。顯然，那是從贊吉爾手中偷來的!$B$B沒錯，我說的就是那個『流亡者』贊吉爾，他因為研究亡靈巫術而被他的部族趕了出去。$B$B那幫荊棘谷分公司的傢伙拿到毒藥之後就開始互相實驗，結果可想而知。' WHERE entry=1138; /* Text0_0: About five months ago, the Venture Co.\'s Stranglethorn division got their hands on a special poison from a shady merchant in Booty Bay named Crank Fizzlebub. Fizzlebub had apparently stolen the poison from Zanzil!$B$BYes, Zanzil the Outcast - the troll that was exiled from his own tribe due to the nature of his \'experiments\' in necromancy.$B$BNaturally, once they had the poison, they proceeded to test it on each other. The results were disastrous. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='大工頭普茲克·加里維克斯在那件事情發生之後就把剩餘的毒藥帶到了他在淤泥沼澤的塔中繼續進行研究，主要是想要解決毒藥的不穩定性。最後他決定和迪菲亞兄弟會達成協議，共同研製開發這種毒藥，代價是由迪菲亞兄弟會提供批量的成品毒藥。$B$B迪菲亞兄弟會的克拉文·摩特維克負責對贊吉爾的毒藥進行改良。' WHERE entry=1158; /* Text0_0: Grand Foreman Puzik Gallywix finally intervened, taking the surplus of poisons to his tower, here at the Sludge Fen, in order to study and research the unstable nature of the toxins. A decision was finally reached to share the secret of the poison with the Defias Brotherhood in exchange for a very large supply of a stable, usable poison.$B$BKlaven Mortwake of the Defias Brotherhood was tasked with the job of altering the chemical properties of Zanzil\'s mixture. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='接下來就是你看到的情況了:毒藥發揮了預期的作用，喝下毒藥的人都變成了被人控制的行屍走人，然而，這種毒藥非常不穩定。$B$B加里維克斯，還有這座塔裡裡外外的人都已經感染了這種毒藥。我們的意志和身體都在不斷被侵襲。我們的器官變得越來越脆弱。$n，我已經無力去拯救這裡的人了，而且我感覺自己馬上要變成他們的一份子了。' WHERE entry=1159; /* Text0_0: Fast forward to the present: The resultant formula works, allowing for the creation of a more controlled drone, however, the drawback is that the inactive compound is extremely volatile.$B$BGallywix, everyone in this tower and everyone outside are infected with the poison. It\'s affecting our minds and our bodies. Our internal organs have become soft and extremely fragile. This is your chance, $N. I don\'t have the strength to carry on and I sense that soon I will become one of \'them.\' */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='我希望你是因為好事才打斷我的，我正在做一些重要的工作。',Text0_1_loc5='我希望你是因為好事才打斷我的，我正在做一些重要的工作。' WHERE entry=1202; /* Text0_0: I hope that your interruption is for a good cause, I was in the middle of some important work. */ /* Text0_1: I hope that your interruption is for a good cause, I was in the middle of some important work. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你也是草藥師嗎，嗯...我想你的水準應該還沒有我這麼棒，那讓我來教你一點專業的技巧吧。',Text0_1_loc5='你也是草藥師嗎，嗯...我想你的水準應該還沒有我這麼棒，那讓我來教你一點專業的技巧吧。' WHERE entry=1203; /* Text0_0: Another Herbalist, hmm. I doubt your skill is as great as my own so perhaps I can train you in a few proper techniques. */ /* Text0_1: Another Herbalist, hmm. I doubt your skill is as great as my own so perhaps I can train you in a few proper techniques. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='啊，一個漁夫。你想要接受訓練嗎?也許我能教你些東西?',Text0_1_loc5='啊，一個漁夫。你想要接受訓練嗎?也許我能教你些東西?' WHERE entry=1205; /* Text0_0: Ah, a fellow Fisherman. Are you perhaps in need of a little training? Maybe I can show you a thing or two? */ /* Text0_1: Ah, a fellow Fisherman. Are you perhaps in need of a little training? Maybe I can show you a thing or two? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='歡迎來暴風城。我們可是花了很長時間才將它重建起來的，但是這些工作都很值得。那麼，你是來參觀的還是有任務在身?',Text0_1_loc5='歡迎來暴風城。我們可是花了很長時間才將它重建起來的，但是這些工作都很值得。那麼，你是來參觀的還是有任務在身?' WHERE entry=1206; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Stormwind. Took a long time to rebuild her but it was well worth it. So are you visiting, or are you here on business? */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to Stormwind. Took a long time to rebuild her but it was well worth it. So are you visiting, or are you here on business? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='找我學習烹飪的學徒並不多，如果你準備好了的話，我馬上就可以教你一些烹飪技巧。',Text0_1_loc5='找我學習烹飪的學徒並不多，如果你準備好了的話，我馬上就可以教你一些烹飪技巧。' WHERE entry=1207; /* Text0_0: I don\'t get too many cooks in here looking for training, but I guess I could teach you something if you\'re ready. */ /* Text0_1: I don\'t get too many cooks in here looking for training, but I guess I could teach you something if you\'re ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='我看起來像是那種閑得可以招待每個旅行者的人嗎?快點告訴我你需要什麼，我可沒有時間和你慢慢磨蹭。',Text0_1_loc5='我看起來像是那種閑得可以招待每個旅行者的人嗎?快點告訴我你需要什麼，我可沒有時間和你慢慢磨蹭。' WHERE entry=1208; /* Text0_0: Do I look like I have the time or energy to coddle every tourist that wanders through my door? Tell me what you need, and make it quick. */ /* Text0_1: Do I look like I have the time or energy to coddle every tourist that wanders through my door? Tell me what you need, and make it quick. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='找我學習剝皮的學徒並不多，如果你準備好了，我馬上就可以教你一些東西。',Text0_1_loc5='找我學習剝皮的學徒並不多，如果你準備好了，我馬上就可以教你一些東西。' WHERE entry=1210; /* Text0_0: I don\'t get too many Skinners in here looking for training, but I guess I could teach you something if you\'re ready. */ /* Text0_1: I don\'t get too many Skinners in here looking for training, but I guess I could teach you something if you\'re ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='雖然現在是和平時期，但是我們可不能荒廢了我們的戰鬥技能!',Text0_1_loc5='雖然現在是和平時期，但是我們可不能荒廢了我們的戰鬥技能!' WHERE entry=1215; /* Text0_0: The big wars might be over, for now, but we still have to keep our skills sharp! */ /* Text0_1: The big wars might be over, for now, but we still have to keep our skills sharp! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='暴風城是人類的支柱，它是建立在鋼鐵的意志和鋒利的刀刃上的。',Text0_1_loc5='暴風城是人類的支柱，它是建立在鋼鐵的意志和鋒利的刀刃上的。' WHERE entry=1216; /* Text0_0: Stormwind is the pillar of the human race, maintained through strength of will and the edge of a sturdy blade. */ /* Text0_1: Stormwind is the pillar of the human race, maintained through strength of will and the edge of a sturdy blade. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='你好。你想要學一些戰鬥技巧嗎?',Text0_1_loc5='你好。你想要學一些戰鬥技巧嗎?' WHERE entry=1217; /* Text0_0: Greetings.  You seek instruction in the art of war? */ /* Text0_1: Greetings.  Do you seek instruction in art of war? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='活到老，學到老。',Text0_1_loc5='活到老，學到老。' WHERE entry=1218; /* Text0_0: No matter how much one learns, there is always more to know. */ /* Text0_1: No matter how much one learns, there is always more to know. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='戰士的任務之一就是保護。正如我們在戰場上保護自己的同伴一樣，我們要時刻保護被遺忘者的利益。',Text0_1_loc5='戰士的任務之一就是保護。正如我們在戰場上保護自己的同伴一樣，我們要時刻保護被遺忘者的利益。' WHERE entry=1219; /* Text0_0: The warrior\'s role is one of protection.  Just as we protect our compatriots in battle, we must also protect the interests of the Forsaken. */ /* Text0_1: The warrior\'s role is one of protection.  Just as we protect our compatriots in battle, we must also protect the interests of the Forsaken. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='哦，一個同夥的治療師。我願意傳授任何能幫助你旅途的東西。',Text0_1_loc5='哦，一個同夥的治療師。我願意傳授任何能幫助你旅途的東西。' WHERE entry=1220; /* Text0_0: Oh, a fellow Physician. I would be glad to teach you anything that would aid your journeys. */ /* Text0_1: Oh, a fellow Physician. I would be glad to teach you anything that would aid your journeys. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='怎麼了，$g小夥子:姑娘;?我能幫你什麼忙嗎?',Text0_1_loc5='怎麼了，$g小夥子:姑娘;?我能幫你什麼忙嗎?' WHERE entry=1221; /* Text0_0: Yes my $g son : daughter;? What can I assist you with? */ /* Text0_1: Yes my $g son : daughter;? What can I assist you with? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='我從鐵爐堡來到這裡協助進行重建工作。我希望能向你傳授盡可能多的本領，然後我就能回家去，把這堆事情丟給你來做。',Text0_1_loc5='我從鐵爐堡來到這裡協助進行重建工作。我希望能向你傳授盡可能多的本領，然後我就能回家去，把這堆事情丟給你來做。' WHERE entry=1225; /* Text0_0: I came from Ironforge to help out with the rebuilding effort here. If I can teach enough of ye my skills then maybe I can leave it to ye and take myself back home. */ /* Text0_1: I came from Ironforge to help out with the rebuilding effort here. If I can teach enough of ye my skills then maybe I can leave it to ye and take myself back home. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='什麼?你打擾我了，你最好趕快找到一個說得過去的理由。',Text0_1_loc5='什麼?你打擾我了，你最好趕快找到一個說得過去的理由。' WHERE entry=1226; /* Text0_0: Yeah? Ye interrupted me, so ye better have a blasted good reason to do so. */ /* Text0_1: Yeah? Ye interrupted me, so ye better have a blasted good reason to do so. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='在達拉然陷落和奎爾薩拉斯被摧毀之後，這樣的東西就很難在世面上看到了。但是魯坎·考迪爾和我的其他一些商業夥伴很好的完成了我的訂單。',Text0_1_loc5='在達拉然陷落和奎爾薩拉斯被摧毀之後，這樣的東西就很難在世面上看到了。但是魯坎·考迪爾和我的其他一些商業夥伴很好的完成了我的訂單。',Text1_0_loc5='我這裡賣的可都是由暴風城最好的工匠和法師製作東西，世上最好的魔法裝備!',Text1_1_loc5='我這裡賣的可都是由暴風城最好的工匠和法師製作東西，世上最好的魔法裝備!' WHERE entry=1231; /* Text0_0: Since the fall of Dalaran and the destruction of Quel\'Thalas, wares of this sort have been hard to come by. But Lucan Cordell and some of our other Tradesman have been doing a fine job of filling our orders with quality merchandise. */ /* Text0_1: Since the fall of Dalaran and the destruction of Quel\'Thalas, wares of this sort have been hard to come by. But Lucan Cordell and some of our other Tradesman have been doing a fine job of filling our orders with quality merchandise. */ /* Text1_0: I sell only the finest arcane gear, made by the crafters and mages here in the city of Stormwind. */ /* Text1_1: I sell only the finest arcane gear, made by the crafters and mages here in the city of Stormwind. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='在達拉然陷落和奎爾薩拉斯被摧毀之後，這樣的東西就很難在世面上看到了。但是魯坎·考迪爾和我的其他一些商業夥伴很好的完成了我的訂單。',Text0_1_loc5='在達拉然陷落和奎爾薩拉斯被摧毀之後，這樣的東西就很難在世面上看到了。但是魯坎·考迪爾和我的其他一些商業夥伴很好的完成了我的訂單。',Text1_0_loc5='我這裡賣的可都是由暴風城最好的工匠和法師製作東西，世上最好的魔法裝備!',Text1_1_loc5='我這裡賣的可都是由暴風城最好的工匠和法師製作東西，世上最好的魔法裝備!' WHERE entry=1232; /* Text0_0: Since the fall of Dalaran and the destruction of Quel\'Thalas, wares of this sort have been hard to come by. But Lucan Cordell and some of our other Tradesman have been doing a fine job of filling our orders with quality merchandise. */ /* Text0_1: Since the fall of Dalaran and the destruction of Quel\'Thalas, wares of this sort have been hard to come by. But Lucan Cordell and some of our other Tradesman have been doing a fine job of filling our orders with quality merchandise. */ /* Text1_0: I sell only the finest arcane gear, made by the crafters and mages here in the city of Stormwind. */ /* Text1_1: I sell only the finest arcane gear, made by the crafters and mages here in the city of Stormwind. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='為了增進夜精靈和人類的聯盟關係，我千里迢迢帶來了由泰達希爾最好的工匠製作的東西。我這裡的東西應有盡有，請隨意挑選。',Text0_1_loc5='為了增進夜精靈和人類的聯盟關係，我千里迢迢帶來了由泰達希爾最好的工匠製作的東西。我這裡的東西應有盡有，請隨意挑選。' WHERE entry=1233; /* Text0_0: Made by the finest craftsmen in all of Teldrassil, carried by hand from Kalimdor to Azeroth as a sign of the growing alliance between the people of the Great Tree and the humans of this land. If there is anything you require, you have but to ask. */ /* Text0_1: Made by the finest craftsmen in all of Teldrassil, carried by hand from Kalimdor to Azeroth as a sign of the growing alliance between the people of the Great Tree and the humans of this land. If there is anything you require, you have but to ask. */
