UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc5='暴風城最好的貨物啊，朋友，你絕對不應該錯過。看看有什麼你需要的東西嗎?',Text0_1_loc5='暴風城最好的貨物啊，朋友，你絕對不應該錯過。看看有什麼你需要的東西嗎?',Text1_0_loc5='暴風城最好的貨物啊，朋友，你絕對不應該錯過。看看有什麼你需要的東西嗎?',Text1_1_loc5='暴風城最好的貨物啊，朋友，你絕對不應該錯過。看看有什麼你需要的東西嗎?' WHERE entry=1235; /* Text0_0: Best deals in all of Stormwind my friend, won\'t find any better. Now, what can I help you with? */ /* Text0_1: Best deals in all of Stormwind my friend, won\'t find any better. Now, what can I help you with? */ /* Text1_0: Best deals in all of Stormwind my friend, won\'t find any better. Now, what can I help you with? */ /* Text1_1: Best deals in all of Stormwind my friend, won\'t find any better. Now, what can I help you with? */
